messages.text: Ryan? What’s up? It’s so late
I’m following Charlotte. She went into the park!
Big black trees and weird noises
Wait, isn’t there a full moon tonight??
Are you CRAZY? What are you doing outside?
You’re a WEREWOLF! You’ll change and hurt her!
No I would never do that, even when I’m changed
You’ll get into all sorts of trouble though!
Why are you following her anyway??
I told you last time, I think she might be cheating on me
A 3am stroll in the park is not promising, that’s true
But why do you think otherwise?
Well during full moon time we … stay away
She knows you’re a werewolf, right?
But obviously we keep away during those days just to be sure
So I thought everything was going great
But then Jack told me he saw her go into the park
Yeah, my buddy the vampire, remember?
Ah, yes. He tried to take me for a ‘bloody mary’ once
Haha lol he cracks me up
Well it’s not funny! I’m trying to stay human thank you
Anyway, he was flying around at night
No he got distracted by a group of drunk kids
That must be a party for him
So what is she doing in the park?
Idk but I decided I need to find out
Yes. I’ve been following her from her place to the park
I mean, for you! You don’t want to get caught in the moonlight!
Although you did seem to recognize me
I’m positive I wouldn’t hurt anyone I love!
Why would she go to the forest to cheat on you?
You’re staying apart anyway, during the full moon
Yeah, one of them went by me, pretty close
What, are they having a multiple date?
You’re just full of great thoughts
Idk … they gathered in this clearing
I can’t go too close or I’ll be in the light …
There’s a thin layer of clouds but I don’t want to risk it
Like, literally rubbed her head against this dude
Sorry dude, that sounds pretty intimate
And sort of droning or something
Oh, is she in a cult?
They’re kind of swatting at the moon
But it’s my Charlotte! How could she do this to me!
It’s not easy being a werewolf’s girlfriend …
Maybe she’s just letting some steam out
Ugh why do I even talk to you?
Cause I’m your only normal human friend :)
Charlotte just looked in my direction and her eyes WERE GREEN
I think she might see me if I move
Yeah, I’ve tried to make it as dark as possible
Damn, run! If she’s in a cult she won’t be happy to see you spying on her
Moon came all the way out
They’re werewolves? Why would she hide that from you?
They’ve all turned into scary cats!!
Why? I mean, you’re a werewolf, you should understand this
Exactly … I’m a wereWOLF … and they are wereCATS
It’s coming … I want at them … to tear them up!!
Holy shit. Get deeper into the forest!! Into the shadow!
Too late … I just stepped out into the mo
Did you change?? Don’t hurt them!
I saw Charlotte, and my werewolf mind KNEW
Not only that, I just stopped and looked at her
Yup. And as we got closer, we started to change
Until I was suddenly me, holding a human Charlotte
Love was stronger …  Amazing! So no one got hurt?
What? Wait what about the other werecats?
Oh yeah, they’re furious. They’re hunting us right now
We’re running! Terrified, but happy. Talk to you later!
